data.description: No sign on property, parking is behind home! Tons of room in this home with country charm. Front covered porch, also side covered deck.  Enjoy the Alder Creek in your back yard, Salmon fish ladder below.  The seller is still working on cleaning up the home and yard.  New Roof 2012, newly refinished floors, some new paint, Home has an unfinished basement could be finished for more living space, possible 5th bedroom downstairs non-conforming.
